    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rival explorers have unleashed <i>The Curse </i>while looting a sacred tomb!<br>The Curse latches on to one of them, mutating them into a demon, and draining them of life!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893050/extras/8770d48b08a871cb8975b6ecc2cc8d29.poster.avif?t=1673839203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893050/extras/8770d48b08a871cb8975b6ecc2cc8d29.webm?t=1673839203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893050/extras/8770d48b08a871cb8975b6ecc2cc8d29.mp4?t=1673839203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The only chance of survival for the inflicted is to catch another explorer and cast The Curse onto them before time runs out!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893050/extras/bdaa48cd9e57e09b210657d19c6a02af.poster.avif?t=1673839203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893050/extras/bdaa48cd9e57e09b210657d19c6a02af.webm?t=1673839203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893050/extras/bdaa48cd9e57e09b210657d19c6a02af.mp4?t=1673839203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The explorers' only hope is to evade the Demon while repairing their elevator to escape.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893050/extras/d1311084023ce8e97bf73e8012ed47ae.poster.avif?t=1673839203\" width=600 height=338 ><source s